{
  "stem": "24163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, in my first or second year of school, my parents decided, as I said, to move to the town-- city of Gelsenkirchen, which was practically adjacent to Essen Katernberg, maybe approximately eight miles, at the most.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, I entered a-- a Jewish day school, a Jewish school-- [GERMAN] was the name of it, and until I was old enough to go to high school, a German high school.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went there through classes, [GERMAN], about almost five years of high school, practically the equivalent of a-- an American high school education.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that lasted until the middle '30s, when relatives who had arrived in the United States and lived in the city of Chicago wrote to my parents and said it would be advisable to take Herman out of school, so he would learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if he get-- comes to the United States, eventually, hopefully-- which were our intentions already in the mid '30s-- that he would have-- immediately have a job.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if he learns a trade, he will have a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if he doesn't have a trade, its most difficult to find employment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my parents decided to take me out of the German high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I became apprentice-- an apprentice in a tailor shop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's the period in his life he remarried.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe it might have been 1928.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my-- our stepmother-- well, for a while, our grandmother, our fraternal grandmother, what lived with us, raised both my brother and me, with the-- with the help of a-- a governess.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father then decided to remarry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our stepmother-- her name was Theresa-- she-- she then continued to raise us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Initially, I think, they were pretty good.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
